title: 166: The Target Haul Episode  (March '22 Edition)
itunes:title: The Target Haul Episode  (March '22 Edition)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and the gang taste test 14 AMAZING finds from Target and not one got a score under 7.5 from Lisa. What did they try? Happy you asked! An amazing dessert hummus, another stellar find from the Tattooed Chef, tasty sparkling water, a killer fruity salsa, the best cauliflower Buffalo wings ever, something new from Clif, and so much more! Plus, a really fun find from Cheetos that you have to try ASAP! So wait no longer, push play, then head on over to our Foodcast Page for a list of all the products mentioned in the episode.
itunes:summary: We’re not kidding, this is the BEST TARGET HAUL EVER!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
